ifications 💬 Public anonymous message page 🔗 Custom profile links 🖼️ Avatar upload 💸 100% free forever👉 https://qrypty.com⭐ Boost & share with friends!#privacy #email #anonymous #encryption #infosec #QRYPTY #notracking', 'publication_date': 'Fri, 08 May 2026 01:38:46 +0000', 'source': 'https://mastodon.social/@vynvvyvvn/116536365661635368', 'source_type': "['']", 'source_level': 2, 'text': [], 'observables': {'domain-name': ['qrypty.com'], 'email-addr': ['vynvvyvvn@mastodon.social']}}, {'title': '#infosec #cybersecurity #linux dirty frag is easy to exploit, well done!#copyfail  #dirtyfrag', 'publication_date': 'Fri, 08 May 2026 01:38:46 +0000', 'source': 'https://mastodon.social/@nwcs/116536272662450370', 'source_type': "['']", 'source_level': 2, 'text': [], 'observables': {'email-addr': ['nwcs@mastodon.social']}}, {'title': '#infosec #cybersecurity #linux "dirty frag" without the echo chamber https://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2026/05/07/8#copyfail #dirtyfrag', 'publication_date': 'Fri, 08 May 2026 01:38:46 +0000', 'source': 'https://mastodon.social/@nwcs/116536259426300997', 'source_type': "['']", 'source_level': 2, 'text': [], 'observables': {'domain-name': ['openwall.com'], 'email-addr': ['nwcs@mastodon.social'], 'url': ['http://www.openwall.com']}}, {'title': 'Dirty Frag: a zero-day universal Linux LPEhttps://github.com/V4bel/dirtyfrag/blob/master/assets/write-up.md#infosec', 'publication_date': 'Fri, 08 May 2026 01:38:46 +0000', 'source': 'https://aus.social/@shlee/116536206077309995', 'source_type': "['']", 'source_level': 2, 'text': [], 'observables': {'domain-name': ['github.com', 'social.chinwag.org'], 'email-addr': ['mike@chinwag.org', 'shlee@aus.social']}}, {'title': 'CVE-2026-42880 - ArgoCD ServerSideDiff is vulnerable to Kubernetes Secret Extraction', 'publication_date': 'Thu, 07 May 2026 23:16:32 +0000', 'source': 'https://cvefeed.io/vuln/detail/CVE-2026-42880', 'source_type': "['']", 'source_level': 2, 'text': ["Argo CD is a declarative, GitOps continuous delivery tool for Kubernetes. From versions 3.2.0 to before 3.2.11 and 3.3.0 to before 3.3.9, there is a missing authorization and data-masking gap in Argo CD's ServerSideDiff endpoint that allows an attacker with read-only access to extract plaintext Kubernetes Secret data from etcd via the Kubernetes API server's Server-Side Apply dry-run mechanism. This issue has been patched in versions 3.2.11 and 3.3.9.", 'The following products are affected byCVE-2026-42880vulnerability. Even ifcvefeed.iois aware of the exact versions of the products that are affected, the information is not represented in the table below.', 'Common Attack Pattern Enumeration and Classification (CAPEC) stores attack patterns, which are descriptions of the common attributes and approaches employed by adversaries to exploit theCVE-2026-42880weaknesses.', 'We scan GitHub repositories to detect new proof-of-concept exploits. Following list is a collection of public exploits and proof-of-concepts, which have been published on GitHub (sorted by the most recently updated).', "Vulnerability history details can be useful for understanding the evolution of a vulnerability, and for identifying the most recent changes that may impact the vulnerability's severity, exploitability, or other characteristics."], 'observables': {'email-addr': ['hey@cvefeed.io', 'security-advisories@github.com'], 'url': ['https://github.com/argoproj/argo-cd/security/advisories/GHSA-3v3m-wc6v-x4x3'], 'vulnerability': ['CVE-2026-42880', 'GHSA-3V3M-WC6V-X4X3']}}, {'title': 'CVE-2026-7891 - Mendix Studio Pro Anonymous User Role Inheritance Authorization Bypass', 'publication_date': 'Thu, 07 May 2026 22:16:37 +0000', 'source': 'https://cvefeed.io/vuln/detail/CVE-2026-7891', 'source_type': "['']", 'source_level': 2, 'text': ['The VerySecureApp made by DIVD using Mendix Studio Pro 11.8.0 Beta allows unintended data exposure due to authorization misconfiguration. The VerySecureApp allows anonymous users of the MyFirstModule with the anonymous user role to gain access to all stored records, even though no access rights are explicitly configured on that role. Anonymous users are required to make a Mendix Entity available publicly. All versions of Mendix Studio Pro up to 11.8.0 Beta silently make an Anonymous user role follow user inheritance rules, without mentioning this explicitly in the documentation.', 'The following products are affected byCVE-2026-7891vulnerability. Even ifcvefeed.iois aware of the exact versions of the products that are affected, the information is not represented in the table below.', 'Common Attack Pattern Enumeration and Classification (CAPEC) stores attack patterns, which are descriptions of the common attributes and approaches employed by adversaries to exploit theCVE-2026-7891weaknesses.', 'We scan GitHub repositories to detect new proof-of-concept exploits. Following list is a collection of public exploits and proof-of-concepts, which have been published on GitHub (sorted by the most recently updated).', "Vulnerability history details can be useful for understanding the evolution of a vulnerability, and for identifying the most recent changes that may impact the vulnerability's severity, exploitability, or other characteristics."], 'observables': {'domain-name': ['cvefeed.io'], 'email-addr': ['csirt@divd.nl'], 'url': ['http://www.divd.nl/mendix.html', 'https://csirt.divd.nl/DIVD-2026-00006/', 'https://www.divd.nl/mendix.html'], 'vulnerability': ['CVE-2026-7891']}}, {'title': 'CVE-2026-42826 - Azure DevOps Information Disclosure Vulnerability', 'publication_date': 'Thu, 07 May 2026 22:16:35 +0000', 'source': 'https://cvefeed.io/vuln/detail/CVE-2026-42826', 'source_type': "['']", 'source_level': 2, 'text': ['The following products are affected byCVE-2026-42826vulnerability. Even ifcvefeed.iois aware of the exact versions of the products that are affected, the information is not represented in the table below.', 'Common Attack Pattern Enumeration and Classi